description: ZipWall dust barrier tips…I use 10 foot poles with 4 mil plastic to seal the room. The Foam Rail is awesome, it compresses plastic against ceilings or walls. And this contains dust to one room instead of the entire house 🔥many thanks to @zipwall_llc for sponsoring this tutorial and making great products that keep people safe❤️#drywall #dustbarriersystem #zipwall #brandpartner
